                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110529-106-off614 t18110529-106-crimeloc617"></join>. On the 6th of May I was in the accompting-house; a man and the prisoner came into the shop, I went to them, they ran off, I followed them suspecting that they had taken something. I observed the prisoner drop a bag of shot; I followed him and took him; I gave him in charges of the constable. This is the bag of shot, there is our mark on it.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you ever find out the man - A. No.</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in his defence, nor called any witnesses to character.</p>
